      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hey everyone! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/tada.png?v=14\" title=\":tada:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":tada:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/waving_hand.png?v=14\" title=\":waving_hand:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":waving_hand:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> We’re super excited to announce our brand new <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLOS6HEAssHDkwteZgooMyBc2FOvpWv9TT\">YouTube playlist</a> all about creating recurring tasks and making the most of our app! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/hammer_and_wrench.png?v=14\" title=\":hammer_and_wrench:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":hammer_and_wrench:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/repeat_button.png?v=14\" title=\":repeat_button:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":repeat_button:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Whether you’re a total newbie or a productivity pro, these quick and easy video guides will help you save time, get organized, and maybe even have a little fun along the way!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLOS6HEAssHDkwteZgooMyBc2FOvpWv9TT\">Check it out</a> and happy scheduling! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/date.png?v=14\" title=\":date:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":date:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=14\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/a/ba1c9bd6d56c54f0a1506b04513064123baf6352.jpeg\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-06-16 at 15.36.03\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/a/ba1c9bd6d56c54f0a1506b04513064123baf6352_2_690x371.jpeg\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-06-16 at 15.36.03\" width=\"690\" height=\"371\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-06-16 at 15.36.03</span><span class=\"informations\">1920×1034 125 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
